column1: # For 1908, there are just two monthly readings and an annual total. The monthly values have been omitted.
# The figure for February 1924 includes estimates for 5 days and has been retained.
# The figure for July 1941 was calculated and has been omitted.
# Figures for February, March and December 1955 are estimated and have been omitted.
# All figures for 1960 are estimates and have been omitted.
# The station continued until 1966 according to MIDAS.
